            {
               "text": "### Prerequisites\n\nThis text will explore concepts discussed in the previous text (<htcite0>) to explain the formation of the atom. Therefore, we recommend studying it before continuing.",
               "source": [
                  {
                     "type": 1,
                     "uuid": "e6850f30-71aa-43c3-96b8-c47a81eedcb1",
                     "text": "History Tracers Team",
